image_analysis.description: A photograph of a bedroom featuring blue textured walls and a plaid carpet. The room contains a large bed with a floral patterned headboard and white linens. Flanking the bed are two wooden nightstands with matching lamps. To the right, there are three sets of floor-to-ceiling cream-colored curtains with floral patterns and red tie-backs. On the left, a silver air purifier stands near a dark leather chair. A wooden dresser is visible on the far right.
